Package: embedr
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Version: 1.0.0
Type: Package
Title: Embed Multimedia Files in HTML Documents
Description: A wrapper for the `<audio>` and `<video>` HTML commands in R.
    It allows you to embed multimedia files in HTML documents generated 
    by R using R code instead of raw HTML. Its functions also include
    arguments for including placeholder text instead of embedded multimedia
    files when generating non-HTML documents in R.
